                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Use Montserrat for headings and Inter for body text</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-as-success mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Maintain proper hierarchy with consistent heading levels</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-as-success mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Use JetBrains Mono for code and technical content</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Don'ts</h4>
                        <ul class="space-y-2">
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-as-danger mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Don't mix too many font weights in one section</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-as-danger mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Avoid using fonts not specified in this guide</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-as-danger mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Don't use text smaller than 14px for body content</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

